name: keyring
description: Store and access your passwords safely.

advisories.title: Incorrect Default Permissions in keyring
advisories.description: Python keyring has insecure permissions on new databases, allowing world-readable files to be created.

advisories.title: Incorrect Default Permissions in keyring
advisories.description: Python keyring lib before 0.10 created keyring files with world-readable permissions.

advisories.title: Python Keyring does not securely initialize encryption cipher
advisories.description: Python Keyring 0.9.1 does not securely initialize the cipher when encrypting passwords for `CryptedFileKeyring` files, which makes it easier for local users to obtain passwords via a brute-force attack.
